item.title: Building ReverSEE
item.description: Building ReverSEE This post aims to cover the developement process of ReverSEE, a reverse image search hoopla I built to essentialy learn to use PyTorch. a silly idea popular indian fashion website allows you to throw a picture of a random tshirt in their search bar and they’ll find you how a similar tshirt available in the store. Idea: How could i go about building something similar of my own?
